   "source": [
    "AVAX_last_price\n",
    "ETH_last_price\n",
    "MATIC_last_price\n",
    "\n",
    "# Run the Monte Carlo Simulation\n",
    "for x in range(number_simulations):\n",
    "\n",
    "    print(f\"Running Simulation {x}...\")\n",
    "    \n",
    "    AVAX_price = [AVAX_last_price]\n",
    "    ETH_price = [ETH_last_price]\n",
    "    MATIC_price = [MATIC_last_price]\n",
    "\n",
    "    for n in range(number_records):\n",
    "        \n",
    "        simulated_prices = AVAX_price[-1] * (1 + np.random.normal(avg_daily_return['AVAX-USD'], std_dev_daily_return['AVAX-USD']))\n",
    "        AVAX_price.append(simulated_prices)\n",
    "    \n",
    "        simulated_prices = ETH_price[-1] * (1 + np.random.normal(avg_daily_return['ETH-USD'], std_dev_daily_return['ETH-USD']))\n",
    "        ETH_price.append(simulated_prices)\n",
    "        \n",
    "        simulated_prices = MATIC_price[-1] * (1 + np.random.normal(avg_daily_return['MATIC-USD'], std_dev_daily_return['MATIC-USD']))\n",
    "        MATIC_price.append(simulated_prices)\n",
    "    \n",
    "   # Create a DataFrame of the simulated prices  \n",
    "    portfolio = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "        \"AVAX Simulated Prices\": AVAX_price,\n",
    "        \"ETH Simulated Prices\": ETH_price,\n",
    "        \"MATIC Simulated Prices\": MATIC_price\n",
    "    })\n",
    "    \n",
    "    \n",
    "    portfolio_returns=portfolio.pct_change()   \n",
    "    \n",
    "    weights = [0.33, 0.33, 0.34]\n",
    "    \n",
    "    \n",
    "    weighted_portfolio_returns = portfolio_returns.dot(weights) \n",
    "    \n",
    "    monte_carlo[x] = (1+ weighted_portfolio_returns.fillna(0)).cumprod()"
   ]
  },

   "source": [
    "cumulative_returns = monte_carlo.iloc[-1]\n",
    "confidence_intervals = cumulative_returns.quantile(q=[0.05, 0.95])\n",
    "crypto_returns = cumulative_returns\n",
    "crypto_conf_interval = confidence_intervals\n",
    "\n",
    "crypto_returns.plot(kind='hist', bins=10, title = \"Confidence Interval of Crypto Basket one Portfolio\")\n",
    "plt.axvline(crypto_conf_interval.iloc[0], color='r')\n",
    "plt.axvline(crypto_conf_interval.iloc[1], color='r')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
